        "username": "庆丰包子的梦帝",
        "uid": "1283"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t习近平不是已经连任了吗？还有什么官不官宣的？\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-12-01",
      "agree_count": 5,
      "discussion_count": 4,
